title: JailBreak for iPod Touch(8GB, 16GB, 32GB) (All firmware versions
description:
This is an easy 4 step jailbreak for the ipod touch. I&#039;m sure it would work with the iphone as well. But it has not been tested with an iPhone yet.

This will jailbreak any size iPod Touch, as well as any firmware version, to any version. Each step will bring you up another version. So you can stop at which ever version you want.

This has been tested with success on an iPod Touch 32GB on all firmware versions.

I hope the instructions are simple enough.
